Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.63,0:04:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys! Hurry up-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.04,0:04:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet! Stay quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.81,0:04:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in trouble if they notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.01,0:04:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's the chance! Get on the ship-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.05,0:04:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody, grab an oar and get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.02,0:04:31.76,Sign,,0,0,268,,{\blur0.3\fad(500,0)\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(455,500,\1a&H00&)}Fishman District, Noah
