Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! They'll come after us any minute now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never return to Fishman Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.20,0:04:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and get through the Red Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.01,0:04:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! The Mermaid Café of my dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.38,0:04:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to take just one look at the beautiful Mermaids!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.75,0:04:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let it go, you fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:04:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit yappin' and row like your life depends on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.92,0:05:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! What a disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.12,0:05:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as we got past the sleeping Kraken,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.82,0:05:10.13,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,and made it down 10,000 meters,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:14.67,Sign,,0,0,365,,{\blur0.3\fad(1000,0)\fs60\bord2.2\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(955,1000,\1a&H00&)}South Blue Pirate, "Crab-Hand" Gyro
