Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.13,0:05:12.96,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,we were surrounded by sea monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.96,0:05:14.67,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,And we couldn't even fight back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.44,0:05:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Become the Fishmen's henchmen or die?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.51,0:05:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What kinda choice is that?!\NOf course we chose to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.95,0:05:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.95,0:05:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should we humans become\Nthe Fishmen's henchmen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.95,0:05:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we're moving away from the Mermaid Café!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.43,0:05:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop crying and let's go, guys!\NConsider yourself lucky you're still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.26,0:05:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? They ran away?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.10,0:05:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye, Boss. As soon as my back was turned.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.24,0:06:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So they ran away again-dosun?\NThey never learn, do they-dosun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans always run.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.45,0:06:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I just tear them apart?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.59,0:06:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pain in the butt-ch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.80,0:06:22.50,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,We can just make them into an example, as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.96,0:06:23.67,Sign,,0,0,350,,{\blur0.3\fad(520,0)\fs60\bord2.2\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(475,520,\1a&H00&)}New Fishman Pirates, Captain Hody Jones
