Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.17,0:06:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then allow me to take care of them-ch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.14,0:06:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to go, Ikaros.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Much, understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.58,0:06:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.68,0:06:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.68,0:06:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the bubble ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't take that many power drug pills at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.58,0:07:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.45,0:07:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my place!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.99,0:07:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's huge!
