Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.42,0:08:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm in the water, I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.09,0:08:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,a fashionable starfish, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.89,0:08:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,on Fishman Island, I'm the president
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.96,0:08:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and celebrity designer of Criminal Co.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My brand is known far and wide
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.71,0:08:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and we have stores all over the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.80,0:08:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the famous Doskoi Panda is—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.24,0:08:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, look over there! What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you listening, Straw?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.75,0:08:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The first floor is a Criminal store.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Camie... Camie...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.25,0:08:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:08:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.72,0:08:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to my story...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.96,0:09:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Miss, you're being unreasonable!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.30,0:09:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds like shop assistant's in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe there's a complaint?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.47,0:09:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, everything in this store is overpriced!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.51,0:09:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's really cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.01,0:09:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.68,0:09:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you 10,000 berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.88,0:09:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Miss! That's less than half!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it was her. The complainer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.89,0:09:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.79,0:09:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.96,0:09:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Camie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.29,0:09:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been so long! How've you been?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.23,0:09:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.80,0:09:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Monsieur Pappagu,\Nyou came at just the right time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a troublesome customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.70,0:09:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, so you own this store, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.31,0:09:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's everything so expensive? Are you trying to rip me off?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.58,0:09:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Monsieur!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.21,0:09:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you have to pay a premium for brand name designs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.45,0:09:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a popular designer, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.45,0:10:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I want a discount!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.48,0:10:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We're friends, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe you big time for what you did two years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all free! Take whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.57,0:10:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,For free?! Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.77,0:10:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys! Show no mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.07,0:10:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.07,0:10:23.74,Alt,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.74,0:10:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Monsieur! They took everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.45,0:10:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're merciless!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy for you, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.59,0:10:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There seems to be a commotion outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.39,0:10:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Monsieur! B-Big news!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.09,0:10:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.30,0:10:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I-It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Him{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.34,0:10:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.77,0:10:55.27,Alt,,0,0,0,,It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.11,0:10:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Just look up in the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:11:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He's come down from the royal palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.61,0:11:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Jamon! Jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.22,0:11:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Jamon! Jamon! Jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.82,0:11:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? A whale?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.34,0:11:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would he come to these lowly waters?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.31,0:11:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time I've seen him in person!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.91,0:11:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on? He doesn't even have an escort.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable! He decided to just suddenly come down here on his own?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's a national crisis?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.56,0:11:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't come down here unless it's an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.64,0:12:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's the old guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.77,0:12:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! Don't you know who that is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That man is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.91,0:12:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the king of Fishman Island, or rather, Ryugu Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.65,0:12:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Neptune-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:17.59,Sign,,0,0,365,,{\blur0.3\fad(520,0)\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(475,520,\1a&H00&)}King of Ryugu Kingdom\NNeptune, God of the Sea
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.08,0:12:17.59,Sign,,0,0,365,,{\bord0\blur0.3\fad(520,0)\4a&HFF&}King of Ryugu Kingdom\NNeptune, God of the Sea
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.72,0:12:17.59,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,Neptune!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:20.62,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,Whale!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.69,0:12:20.62,Sign,,0,0,365,,{\blur0.3\fad(520,0)\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(475,520,\1a&H00&)}Hoe (Pet Whale)
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.69,0:12:20.62,Sign,,0,0,365,,{\bord0\blur0.3\fad(520,0)\4a&HFF&}Hoe (Pet Whale)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.62,0:12:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one huge Merman...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.46,0:12:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I prefer Mermaids...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.03,0:12:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What a hairy old guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.05,0:12:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Bow down to him already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What a cute whale!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.47,0:12:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What does he want with those humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.41,0:12:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he personally come down just for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.81,0:12:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Megalo! Are you sure they are the ones-jamon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Didn't we see that shark in the ocean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.96,0:12:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, the one wearing clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.26,0:13:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd been captured by Surume!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.87,0:13:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You, Straw Hat humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.98,0:13:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.11,0:13:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I have come...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.53,0:13:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to invite you to Ryugu Palace-jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.48,0:13:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.48,0:13:47.38,Alt,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu-{\alpha&HFF&}Ryu-Ryu-Ryu-Ryu-Ryugu Palace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.88,0:13:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu-Ryu-{\alpha&HFF&}Ryu-Ryu-Ryu-Ryugu Palace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.19,0:13:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu-Ryu-Ryu-{\alpha&HFF&}Ryu-Ryu-Ryugu Palace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.49,0:13:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu-Ryu-Ryu-Ryu-{\alpha&HFF&}Ryu-Ryugu Palace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.81,0:13:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu-Ryu-Ryu-Ryu-Ryu-{\alpha&HFF&}Ryugu Palace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.46,0:13:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu-Ryu-Ryu-Ryu-Ryu-Ryugu Palace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:47.88,Alt,,0,0,0,,Ryu-{\alpha&HFF&}Ryu-Ryu-Ryu-Ryu-Ryugu Palace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.88,0:13:48.19,Alt,,0,0,0,,Ryu-Ryu-{\alpha&HFF&}Ryu-Ryu-Ryu-Ryugu Palace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.19,0:13:48.49,Alt,,0,0,0,,Ryu-Ryu-Ryu-{\alpha&HFF&}Ryu-Ryu-Ryugu Palace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.49,0:13:48.81,Alt,,0,0,0,,Ryu-Ryu-Ryu-Ryu-{\alpha&HFF&}Ryu-Ryugu Palace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.81,0:13:49.46,Alt,,0,0,0,,Ryu-Ryu-Ryu-Ryu-Ryu-{\alpha&HFF&}Ryugu Palace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.46,0:13:52.15,Alt,,0,0,0,,Ryu-Ryu-Ryu-Ryu-Ryu-Ryugu Palace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.05,0:13:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryugu Palace?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.50,0:14:14.00,Sign,,0,0,365,,{\blur0.3\fad(520,0)\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(475,520,\1a&H00&)}Ryugu Kingdom, Coral Hill
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.50,0:14:14.00,Sign,,0,0,365,,{\bord0\blur0.3\fad(520,0)\4a&HFF&}Ryugu Kingdom, Coral Hill
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:16.81,Sign,,0,0,268,,{\blur0.3\fad(520,0)\c&H000000&\1a&HFF&\t(475,520,\1a&H00&)}Madame Sharley's house
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.10,0:14:16.81,Sign,,0,0,268,,{\bord0\blur0.3\fad(520,0)\4a&HFF&}Madame Sharley's house
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.81,0:14:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! Your pulse is getting back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.11,0:14:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.78,0:14:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to thank those two for donating blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.98,0:14:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.99,0:14:30.52,Flashback,,0,0,0,,It's okay, silly! {Flashback} {529}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:33.76,Flashback,,0,0,0,,If you want, we can give you more, silly! {Flashback END} {529}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.33,0:14:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful, but I wanna forget about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.26,0:14:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It would've been crazy if you died of blood loss\Nbefore we found Nami and Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.64,0:14:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Robin-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:14:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! Sanji's in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.32,0:15:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, come here! Splash! Splatta!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.75,0:15:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? Do you need our blood again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.12,0:15:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's so, just tell us! You can have...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.93,0:15:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,As much as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.93,0:15:12.13,Alt,,0,0,0,,As much as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.90,0:15:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to stay calm, silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.17,0:15:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll stay here and...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.47,0:15:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.47,0:15:22.37,Alt,,0,0,0,,Take care of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.37,0:15:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be shy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.78,0:15:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay calm—it's bad for your health!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.48,0:15:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are the worst for my health!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.48,0:15:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so shy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.02,0:15:33.18,Alt,,0,0,0,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.18,0:15:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.19,0:15:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away, fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.36,0:15:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu-{\alpha&HFF&}Ryu-Ryu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.98,0:15:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu-Ryu-{\alpha&HFF&}Ryu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.78,0:15:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu-Ryu-Ryu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu-{\alpha&HFF&}Ryu-Ryu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.05,0:15:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu-Ryu-{\alpha&HFF&}Ryu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.77,0:15:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu-Ryu-Ryu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryugu Palace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:47.13,Alt,,0,0,0,,Ryugu Palace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right-jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.10,0:15:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.10,0:15:51.27,Alt,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.40,0:15:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe they were invited to the palace...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.77,0:15:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are those humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.81,0:16:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,King Neptune came to pick them up himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.34,0:16:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They know Monsieur Pappagu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they're famous...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.55,0:16:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, that's Soul King!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.12,0:16:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.85,0:16:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What's Ryugu Palace?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.09,0:16:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! You don't know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.73,0:16:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,To those of us in Ryugu Kingdom,\Nthat place is like a holy land!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.67,0:16:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A heavenly realm ordinary people\Nare not to set foot on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryugu Palace is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.57,0:16:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the place where King Neptune, the three Neptune Brothers,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.08,0:16:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Mermaid Princess live—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.92,0:16:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the royal palace of Ryugu Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.99,0:16:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.99,0:16:45.46,Alt,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.16,0:16:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Camie, you did it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.02,0:16:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmm... So, old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.59,0:16:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call him that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.56,0:16:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there lots of good food at Ryugu Palace?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.83,0:16:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.53,0:17:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. We are prepared for a banquet-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah? I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.18,0:17:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to see Ryugu Palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.81,0:17:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart is filled with anticipation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.38,0:17:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't have a heart to be filled!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.59,0:17:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryugu Palace...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.70,0:17:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I can already smell the treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.52,0:17:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew that'd be your motivation!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.23,0:17:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.10,0:17:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmm. Very well then, Megalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.30,0:17:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Give the Straw Hat humans\Na ride to Ryugu Palace-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.34,0:17:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I get on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.98,0:17:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.78,0:17:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we gonna meet the Mermaid Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.52,0:17:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing? Come with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Well, we don't deserve to go to Ryugu Palace...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:17:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop grumbling and come! Let's have a banquet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.67,0:18:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't just say goodbye here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.77,0:18:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that alright, gramps?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just call him "gramps"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Your friends can come-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.48,0:18:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.18,0:18:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Gramps, you're quite reasonable!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.41,0:18:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, that person is... You guys... really... please!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.25,0:18:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,To Ryugu Palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.76,0:18:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.37,0:18:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Go faster-chin! They'll come any minute now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.60,0:18:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to catch a current in the deep sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why we should've had\Npaddle wheels installed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that the New World is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.45,0:18:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.18,0:18:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.15,0:18:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.62,0:19:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hody Jones!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.73,0:19:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way! He found us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.50,0:19:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What? He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.17,0:19:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What the? He has handcuffs on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.74,0:19:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! He's gonna fight us, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He vanished!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.18,0:19:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd that bastard go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.70,0:19:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.94,0:19:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We've taken damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.47,0:19:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He's too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here on the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.90,0:20:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Take him out! He's only one man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.88,0:20:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! It didn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.45,0:20:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I've fought a Fishman before!\NI had to go through hell to get here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.45,0:20:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You're only a fish!\NDon't mess with us humans, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.16,0:20:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.83,0:20:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, we sure got our hands on something real nice-ch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.45,0:21:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This power drug—Energy Steroids!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.72,0:21:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Fishmen are born\Nten times stronger than humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.02,0:21:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But once we take one Energy Steroid, our physical strength doubles.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.73,0:21:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's twenty times stronger than humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.90,0:21:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If we take two, it'll double {\i1}again{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.27,0:21:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The price for this dreamlike power is the shortening of our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.27,0:21:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,However, we're not afraid of dying—\Nas long as it helps furthering our cause!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.05,0:21:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's he doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.55,0:21:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he gonna do with that mast?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.12,0:21:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why he's in handcuffs!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.72,0:21:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to show us he can sink us\Nwithout even using his hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.33,0:21:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans killed Fisher Tiger and crushed Arlong's ambition!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.10,0:21:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The dark and pitiful history\Nof the Fishmen will end with our generation!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.34,0:22:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We, the New Fishman Pirates, will make that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.99,0:22:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Take them up into the New World\Nand set them adrift.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.73,0:22:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, goodness... You didn't kill them all, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.17,0:22:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I need them alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.34,0:22:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Let your scarred hearts and bodies\Nbe a message to everyone on the surface!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.91,0:22:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell them what you experienced in the depths!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.35,0:22:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell them who did this to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.75,0:22:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Let the humans fear us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.19,0:22:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take the center of the world, Fishman Island,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.59,0:22:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,from that pathetic God of the Sea, Neptune,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.16,0:23:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and drag you humans down into the dark depths of the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.50,0:23:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll all learn that Fishmen\Nare the supreme race!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.62,0:23:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,At the invitation of Fishman Island's king, Neptune,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.59,0:23:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy's group makes their way\Nto a banquet at Ryugu Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.79,0:23:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Luffy's hunger gets the better of him\Nand as soon as he smells food,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.26,0:23:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,he separates from the group.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.60,0:23:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy then discovers a gigantic tower\Nsealed by a door stuck with swords and axes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.70,0:23:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.07,0:23:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ryugu Palace!\NTaken by the Shark They Saved"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.84,0:23:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
